---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy - MATCHS"
  description="Privacy Policy for MATCHS - Local Experiences in Tokyo Tama"
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Last updated: May 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="content-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, including your name, email address, and payment information when you book an experience. We also automatically collect certain information about your device and usage of our website.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to process bookings, communicate with you about your experiences, improve our services, and send marketing communications with your consent. We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
          <p>We share your information with experience providers only as necessary to fulfill your booking. We use third-party payment processors (Stripe) and analytics services (Google Analytics) that may have access to certain information.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
          <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. Payment transactions are encrypted using SSL/TLS technology. However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information at any time. You may also opt out of marketing communications. Contact us at hello@matchses.com to exercise these rights.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>6. Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience, analyze site traffic, and understand where our visitors come from. You can control cookie preferences in your browser settings.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>7. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Our services are not directed to individuals under 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-block">
          <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <strong>hello@matchses.com</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl) 0 var(--spacing-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  
  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
  }
  
  .content-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl) 0;
  }
  
  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .content-block {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }
  
  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  
  .content-block p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .content-block a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .content-block a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }
</style>
